quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,61,"And when the two hosts saw each other, the companions of Mûsâ (Moses) said: "
  26,62,"[Mûsâ (Moses)] said: "
  26,63,"Then We revealed to Mûsâ (Moses) (saying): "
  27,34,"She said: "
  27,35,""
  27,36,"So when (the messengers with the present) came to Sulaimân (Solomon), he said: "
  28,7,"And We inspired the mother of Mûsâ (Moses): (telling): "
  28,8,"Then the household of Fir‘aun (Pharaoh) picked him up, that he might become for them an enemy and a (cause of) grief. Verily, Fir‘aun (Pharaoh), Hâmân and their hosts were sinners."
  28,9,"And the wife of Fir‘aun (Pharaoh) said: "